      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "FAST EDDIE (2) racing well without winning, placing at his last five runs. Last time finished 3rd in a Grade 4/5 on April 2 over 390m at this track behind ABODE'S TRILOGY beaten 3.5 lengths (21.93). Has a solid record from this box including two wins and a minor placing. Top prospect. CASH HANDY (1) is worth forgiving last start after finishing seventh (31.15) from Box 3 at Q Parklands over 520m. Should be in this for a long way. OXIDISATION (8) showed little early speed at her last couple, the latest finishing seventh (20.20) in a Grade 3/4 at Capalaba. Form here at the trip sound including eight wins. Solid formlines coming through her last run. A forward showing wouldn't surprise. ABODE'S TRILOGY (7) is a course and distance winner with definite claims.",
